    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E92 M3, powered by the high-revving S65 4.0L V8 featuring individual throttle bodies and an 8,400 RPM redline. This example is optimized for performance, with recent preventative maintenance including treated rod bearings and upgraded throttle actuators to ensure the longevity of the rotating assembly. The 6-speed manual transmission provides a direct interface to the M Variable Differential Lock, maintaining exceptional lateral grip and power delivery. The chassis remains rigid with no subframe issues, and the suspension geometry is dialed for precision. While the exterior shows honest signs of road use, the drivetrain and hydraulic steering rack remain sharp, offering the visceral feedback expected of a true M-division product.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
