      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Up for sale is a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This power unit utilizes individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing to produce an exceptional power-to-weight ratio. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a limited-slip differential, providing precise torque vectoring. The suspension geometry remains stock with refreshed bushings to maintain factory kinematics. Critically, the rear subframe has been reinforced, and the rod bearings were replaced as preventative maintenance to ensure longevity. This example represents a mechanically sound platform with a crisp throttle response and a rigid chassis, ready for spirited canyon carving or track day duty.",
